---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About AI-Nexus">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8">About AI-Nexus</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      AI-Nexus is a curated index of open-source artificial intelligence models and tools. Our mission is to provide a high-quality, authoritative resource for developers, researchers, and anyone interested in the latest advancements in AI.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-4">
      We believe that open-source is the key to innovation and progress in the field of AI. By providing a centralized and well-organized directory of open-source AI resources, we hope to foster collaboration and accelerate the development of new and exciting AI applications.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
